<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>시그널 봇</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f4efe6;
        --panel: rgba(255, 250, 241, 0.82);
        --ink: #13212e;
        --muted: #617080;
        --accent: #cf5c36;
        --accent-2: #1e847f;
        --accent-3: #c7a84f;
        --danger: #912f40;
        --border: rgba(19, 33, 46, 0.12);
        --shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(19, 33, 46, 0.08);
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "IBM Plex Sans", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        color: var(--ink);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(207, 92, 54, 0.15), transparent 28%),
          radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(30, 132, 127, 0.16), transparent 22%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, #fff7ec 0%, #f4efe6 100%);
      }

      .page {
        max-width: 1280px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 32px 20px 72px;
      }

      .hero {
        display: grid;
        gap: 20px;
        grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr;
        align-items: stretch;
      }

      .hero-main,
      .hero-side,
      .panel,
      .symbol-card {
        background: var(--panel);
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 24px;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .hero-main {
        padding: 28px;
      }

      .hero-side {
        padding: 24px;
        display: grid;
        gap: 14px;
      }

      h1,
      h2,
      h3,
      p {
        margin: 0;
      }

      h1 {
        font-family: "IBM Plex Serif", Georgia, serif;
        font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.4rem);
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
        line-height: 0.95;
      }

      h2 {
        font-family: "IBM Plex Serif", Georgia, serif;
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      .subtle {
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .stat-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 14px;
        margin-top: 28px;
      }

      .stat {
        padding: 16px;
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.58);
        border: 1px solid rgba(19, 33, 46, 0.08);
      }

      .stat strong {
        display: block;
        font-size: 1.7rem;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }

      .section {
        margin-top: 26px;
      }

      .panel {
        padding: 22px;
      }

      .grid-2 {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 18px;
      }

      .grid-3 {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 18px;
      }

      table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
      }

      th,
      td {
        padding: 10px 0;
        text-align: left;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(19, 33, 46, 0.08);
        vertical-align: top;
      }

      th {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .symbol-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 18px;
      }

      .symbol-card {
        padding: 20px;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .symbol-card::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: auto -30px -30px auto;
        width: 120px;
        height: 120px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(207, 92, 54, 0.18), transparent);
      }

      .symbol-header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }

      .symbol-header strong {
        display: block;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
      }

      .score {
        text-align: right;
      }

      .score strong {
        font-size: 2rem;
        line-height: 1;
      }

      .badge-row,
      .metric-row {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .badge {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 6px 10px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        border: 1px solid transparent;
      }

      .badge-positive {
        background: rgba(30, 132, 127, 0.1);
        color: var(--accent-2);
        border-color: rgba(30, 132, 127, 0.16);
      }

      .badge-neutral {
        background: rgba(199, 168, 79, 0.12);
        color: #7a6121;
        border-color: rgba(199, 168, 79, 0.18);
      }

      .badge-negative {
        background: rgba(145, 47, 64, 0.11);
        color: var(--danger);
        border-color: rgba(145, 47, 64, 0.18);
      }

      .metric {
        min-width: 74px;
        padding: 10px 12px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
        border: 1px solid rgba(19, 33, 46, 0.08);
      }

      .metric span {
        display: block;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }

      .sparkline {
        width: 100%;
        height: 68px;
        margin: 12px 0 16px;
      }

      .sparkline polyline {
        fill: none;
        stroke: var(--accent);
        stroke-width: 3;
        stroke-linecap: round;
        stroke-linejoin: round;
      }

      .footer-note {
        margin-top: 20px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.92rem;
      }

      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .hero,
        .grid-2,
        .grid-3,
        .stat-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="page">
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-main">
          <p class="subtle">규칙 기반 관심종목 모니터</p>
          <h1>시그널 봇</h1>
          <p class="subtle" style="margin-top: 14px; max-width: 680px;">
            한국과 미국 관심종목을 매일 점검하고, 설명 가능한 기술적 신호와
            모멘텀 변화만 추려서 보여주는 리포트입니다.
          </p>
          <div class="stat-grid">
            <div class="stat">
              <strong>{{ total_symbols }}</strong>
              <span class="subtle">점검 종목</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <strong>{{ signal_count }}</strong>
              <span class="subtle">신호 발생 종목</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <strong>{{ bullish_count }}</strong>
              <span class="subtle">강세</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <strong>{{ bearish_count }}</strong>
              <span class="subtle">약세</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <aside class="hero-side">
          <div>
            <p class="subtle">기준일</p>
            <h2 style="margin: 6px 0 0;">{{ as_of }}</h2>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="subtle">종목 수집 실패</p>
            <h2 style="margin: 6px 0 0;">{{ failures|length }}</h2>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="subtle">벤치마크 수집 실패</p>
            <h2 style="margin: 6px 0 0;">{{ benchmark_failures|length }}</h2>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </section>

      <section class="section grid-2">
        <div class="panel">
          <h2>오늘 새로 발생한 신호</h2>
          <table>
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>종목</th>
                <th>점수</th>
                <th>신규 이벤트</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              {% if new_signal_rows %}
                {% for row in new_signal_rows[:12] %}
                  <tr>
                    <td>{{ row.symbol }} {{ row.name }}</td>
                    <td>{{ row.score }}</td>
                    <td>{{ row.new_events_label }}</td>
                  </tr>
                {% endfor %}
              {% else %}
                <tr>
                  <td colspan="3" class="subtle">오늘 새로 추가된 이벤트는 없습니다.</td>
                </tr>
              {% endif %}
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <div class="panel">
          <h2>그룹별 요약</h2>
          <table>
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>그룹</th>
                <th>종목 수</th>
                <th>평균 점수</th>
                <th>강세</th>
                <th>약세</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              {% for row in group_summary %}
                <tr>
                  <td>{{ row.group_label }}</td>
                  <td>{{ row.count }}</td>
                  <td>{{ row.avg_score }}</td>
                  <td>{{ row.bullish }}</td>
                  <td>{{ row.bearish }}</td>
                </tr>
              {% endfor %}
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section grid-3">
        <div class="panel">
          <h2>강한 모멘텀</h2>
          <table>
            <tbody>
              {% for card in strong_momentum %}
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <strong>{{ card.symbol }}</strong> {{ card.name }}<br />
                    <span class="subtle">{{ card.state }} | {{ card.events|map(attribute='label')|join(', ') }}</span>
                  </td>
                  <td>{{ card.score }}</td>
                </tr>
              {% endfor %}
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <div class="panel">
          <h2>눌림 관찰 후보</h2>
          <table>
            <tbody>
              {% if pullbacks %}
                {% for card in pullbacks %}
                  <tr>
                    <td>
                      <strong>{{ card.symbol }}</strong> {{ card.name }}<br />
                      <span class="subtle">{{ card.state }}</span>
                    </td>
                    <td>{{ card.score }}</td>
                  </tr>
                {% endfor %}
              {% else %}
                <tr>
                  <td colspan="2" class="subtle">오늘은 상승 추세 눌림 후보가 없습니다.</td>
                </tr>
              {% endif %}
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <div class="panel">
          <h2>약해지는 종목</h2>
          <table>
            <tbody>
              {% for card in weakening %}
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <strong>{{ card.symbol }}</strong> {{ card.name }}<br />
                    <span class="subtle">{{ card.state }} | {{ card.events|map(attribute='label')|join(', ') }}</span>
                  </td>
                  <td>{{ card.score }}</td>
                </tr>
              {% endfor %}
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>종목별 상세 카드</h2>
        <div class="symbol-grid">
          {% for card in all_symbols %}
            <article class="symbol-card">
              <div class="symbol-header">
                <div>
                  <strong>{{ card.symbol }}</strong>
                  <p>{{ card.name }}</p>
                  <p class="subtle">{{ card.market }} | {{ card.group }} | 벤치마크 {{ card.benchmark }}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="score">
                  <strong>{{ card.score }}</strong>
                  <p class="subtle">{{ card.state }}</p>
                  <p class="subtle">신뢰도 {{ card.confidence }}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="subtle">가격 {{ card.price }} | {{ card.source }} | {{ card.data_quality }}</p>
              <svg class="sparkline" viewBox="0 0 220 64" preserveAspectRatio="none">
                <polyline points="{{ card.sparkline_points }}"></polyline>
              </svg>
              <div class="badge-row">
                {% for event in card.events %}
                  <span class="badge {{ event.class_name }}">{{ event.label }}</span>
                {% endfor %}
              </div>
              <div class="metric-row" style="margin-top: 14px;">
                {% for metric in card.metrics %}
                  <div class="metric">
                    <span>{{ metric.label }}</span>
                    <strong>{{ metric.value }}</strong>
                  </div>
                {% endfor %}
              </div>
            </article>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section grid-2">
        <div class="panel">
          <h2>데이터 수집 실패</h2>
          <table>
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>종목</th>
                <th>사유</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              {% if failures %}
                {% for symbol, reason in failures.items() %}
                  <tr>
                    <td>{{ symbol }}</td>
                    <td>{{ reason }}</td>
                  </tr>
                {% endfor %}
              {% else %}
                <tr>
                  <td colspan="2" class="subtle">종목 단위 수집 실패는 없습니다.</td>
                </tr>
              {% endif %}
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <div class="panel">
          <h2>벤치마크 상태</h2>
          <table>
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>벤치마크</th>
                <th>사유</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              {% if benchmark_failures %}
                {% for symbol, reason in benchmark_failures.items() %}
                  <tr>
                    <td>{{ symbol }}</td>
                    <td>{{ reason }}</td>
                  </tr>
                {% endfor %}
              {% else %}
                <tr>
                  <td colspan="2" class="subtle">모든 벤치마크를 정상적으로 수집했습니다.</td>
                </tr>
              {% endif %}
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </section>

      <p class="footer-note">
        이 리포트는 매매 추천이 아니라 우선순위 판단을 돕는 관찰 도구입니다.
        실시간 수집에 실패하면 저장된 캐시 데이터를 사용할 수 있습니다.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
